org.bonitasoft.engine.search
Interface SearchResult<T extends Serializable>

Type Parameters:
T - the type of the objects being returned by the search.
All Superinterfaces:
Serializable
All Known Implementing Classes:
SearchResultImpl
public interface SearchResult<T extends Serializable>
extends Serializable

Represents the result of a Search. For details on 'Search mechanism', see SearchOptionsBuilder and SearchOptions. A SearchResult is composed of a result list getResult() that is the paginated list of results matching the provided criteria, and a result count getCount() that is the total number of results matching the provided criteria.

Author:
Emmanuel Duchastenier, Matthieu Chaffotte, Elias Ricken de Medeiros
See Also:
SearchOptions, SearchOptionsBuilder
